  "body": "I understand that React focuses on the V in MVC but I think the primary focus of a web view is to support interaction by a user. It'd be nice if React had support for input and form validation.\n\nI stumbled across [this StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/a/21857309) that demonstrates some mixins that make it easier to handle user input validation with React. Are there any plans to add more HTML form related tools like the `LinkedStateMixin`? Something official?\n",
